version: v1.0.0
title: JellyGlance v1.0.0
---
Initial release of JellyGlance.

JellyGlance is a modern Jellyfin dashboard for live sessions, recently added media, libraries, users, playback activity, statistics, automation integrations, downloads, webhooks, backups, and first-run setup.

Highlights:
- Live active session cards with stream, device, client, playback, and user details
- Recently Added shelves grouped by Jellyfin library
- Library dashboards with storage, playback, file counts, and manual scan actions
- JellyGlance Users page for Jellyfin, local, and OIDC-ready accounts
- Role management with admin/viewer style access control
- User profile pages with personal wrap-up stats and activity heatmaps
- Statistics dashboard for top media, users, clients, libraries, and watch trends
- Calendar page for Sonarr, Radarr, and Lidarr release planning
- Downloads page for qBittorrent, Transmission, Deluge, SABnzbd, and NZBGet queues
- Magnet links, torrent URLs, and torrent file support
- Integration settings for Jellyfin, Arr apps, Bazarr, and download clients
- Multiple webhook destinations with selectable event triggers
- Background tasks for syncs, imports, health checks, backups, and queue refreshes
- Docker image and Compose setup with /app/config and /app/backups paths
- Safe streamed backup downloads using short-lived signed links
